## Required Fixes

### Fix 1: Remove `parent` Field from All Frontmatter (CRITICAL)
**Files:** All 7 SKILL.md files

Remove lines containing `parent: use-hivemind` from YAML frontmatter of each file.

### Fix 2: Remove `<!-- LOAD-POSITION -->` HTML Comments (HIGH)
**Files:** hivemind-synthesis only

Remove lines 7-11 containing the LOAD-POSITION HTML comment block.

### Fix 3: Convert Second-Person to Imperative Voice (MEDIUM)
**Files:** All 7 SKILL.md files

Transform sentences like:
- "You need this skill when..." → "Load this skill when..."
- "Before you decompose..." → "Before decomposing..."
- "You think the spec is clear..." → "The spec may appear clear..."

### Fix 4: Add Anti-Patterns Section (HIGH)
**Files:** hivemind-system-debug only

The file uses "Do Not Use This For" instead of the standard "Anti-Patterns" section format.

